*Odelo* je bilo od najfinije vune. (The suit was made of the finest wool.)

*Odelom* je obukao sebi novi kaput. (He put on a new coat with his suit.)

On je izvukao *odelo* iz ormana. (He took out the suit from the closet.)

Ona je ukrasila *odelom* svoju sobu. (She decorated her room with her suit.)

On je nosio *odelo* na poslu. (He wore a suit to work.)

Ona je ponela *odelo* na svadbu. (She carried a suit to the wedding.)